  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, oregano, salt, and pepper.",
    "Place the chicken in a shallow baking dish and brush the lemon mixture evenly over both sides of the chicken.",
    "Sprinkle the chopped parsley over the top of the chicken.",
    "Bake the chicken for 25-30 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "While the chicken is baking, heat the glazed olives in a small saucepan over medium heat until warmed through.",
